.max-w-prose
  = doc_info(url: "https://github.com/AaronLasseigne/active_interaction", icon: "cog-6-tooth", icon_css: "text-primary") do
    :markdown
      _Loco_**Motion** encourages keeping business logic out of your
      controllers and models by extracting it into **Service Objects**.

.prose
  :markdown
    # Service Objects

    It is best practice to separate your business logic into **Service
    Objects** rather than shoving all of it into your controllers and models.
    This keeps each layer focused: controllers handle HTTP, models handle
    persistence, and services orchestrate the actual work.

